decks.notes: This Saskia the Unyielding deck focuses on maximizing early aggression and pressure to overwhelm opponents quickly in 1 vs 1 Duel Commander games. The deck includes a wide range of efficient creatures, removal spells, and mana accelerants to establish a strong board presence and maintain tempo throughout the game. By combining aggressive creatures like Goblin Guide, Ghor-Clan Rampager, and Zurgo Bellstriker with powerful removal spells like Lightning Bolt and Terminate, the deck aims to apply consistent pressure and disrupt the opponent's game plan. Additionally, the inclusion of versatile cards like Demonic Tutor and Voice of Resurgence helps ensure the deck can adapt to various situations and maintain a proactive game plan.

mainboard.name: You See a Pair of Goblins
